text: Jungle Rhythm is a Mickey Mouse short animated movie. It was released on November 15, 1929, as part of the Mickey Mouse movie series. It was the thirteenth Mickey Mouse short to be made, the tenth of that year. ==Home media== The short was released on December 7, 2004, on Walt Disney Treasures: Mickey Mouse in Black and White, Volume Two: 1929-1935. ==References== ==Other websites== * * Category:1929 movies Category:Disney animated movies
title: Jungle Rhythm
